node.text:
In the centenary year of the House, Gucci celebrated its Aria collection through a special fashion show held at the Shanghai Exhibition Centre in China, recreating the set and atmosphere of the #GucciAria film, co-directed by @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, which debuted earlier this year in April. 
#AlessandroMichele
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs 
featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to 
the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump "Gucci Gang”
(B. Murray / G. Garcia / G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future “Green Gucci Suit”
(R. Ross / A. Stewart / N. Wilburn / D. Hayes)

Bhad Bhabie “Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)”
(M. McCollum / L. Jae / I. Whitlow / J. Muhammad / L. Porter / D. McCorkell / D. Bregoli / S. Gloade / J. 
Lowe)
Mier “Gucci On My Bag”
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese “Gucci Coochie”
(A. Du Toit / W. Jones / J. Nobrega / L. Muggard / Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw “Waiting For The Stars”
(P. Arbez / D. Shaw/ J. Garraud)

node.title: Gucci Aria Fashion Show in Shanghai

node.text:
Named Hortus Deliciarum (Latin for ‘Garden of Delights’), the new #GucciHighJewelry collection draws on the symbolic motifs that are dear to @alessandro_michele and Gucci, taken from the extensive and multifarious canon of House iconography. The saturated, hypnotic hues of a sky at sunset, the romanticism of a rose garden, and motifs from animal kingdom, evoking mythic bestiary and ancient fauna, are 
the ultimate source of inspiration for the new collection, including more than 130 pieces, mainly one of a kind.

node.title: The New Hortus Deliciarum High Jewelry Collection

node.text: The façade of the #GUCCIGAOK flagship store, designed by artist SeungMo Park @HANDLE, is inspired by an imaginary forest. The artist explores the interplay between light and shadow, and the application of wire netting layers results in a vivid symbolism, illustrating the boundaries between what is real and what is an illusion. Reflecting on the environmental issues of our time, the Park expresses the existence and non-existence of nature, his concerns of what can be lost, leaving only the illusion of what might be left. #AlessandroMichele

node.title: Artist SeungMo Park on creating the #GUCCIGAOK façade

node.text:
Debuting in a special film co-directed by award-winning photographer and director @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, Aria. A singular voice, taking its turn in the spotlight; in the Italian language, ‘air’. In his notes on the collection, the Creative Director calls it “a deep and ecstatic diving in everything we yearningly miss today… a jubilee of breath.” 
In the year of Gucci’s centenary, Alessandro Michele opens the locks of history, only to find a deeply personal vision of the mythology that surrounds the brand. Standing sentinel is the Savoy Club—a tribute to @thesavoylondon hotel where founder Guccio Gucci worked as a liftboy in his youth. Once inside, Aria’s “hacking lab made of incursions and metamorphoses”—from Alessandro Michele’s notes on the show—is unveiled, featuring elements from House heritage and designs from @demnagvasalia, Creative Director of @balenciaga, ultimately expressions of reverence and homage.
#GucciAria #AlessandroMichele 
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump ‘Gucci Gang’
(B. Murray/G. Garcia/G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future ‘Green Gucci Suit’
(R. Ross/A. Stewart/N. Wilburn/D. Hayes)
Bhad Bhabie ‘Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)’
(M. McCollum/L. Jae/I. Whitlow/J. Muhammad/L. Porter/D. McCorkell/D. Bregoli/S. Gloade/J. Lowe)
Mier ‘Gucci On My Bag’
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese ‘Gucci Coochie’
(A. Du Toit/W. Jones/J. Nobrega/L. Muggard/Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw and The Beat ‘Waiting For The Stars’
(P. Arbez/D. Shaw/J. Garraud)
The production of this video followed Health and Safety guidelines and Covid-related laws and regulations.
Bureau Veritas Italia monitored the set in which animals were present and verify that no animals were harmed.

node.text: An intense high-coverage varnish, @guccibeauty’s new plant-based nail lacquers are presented in ten vibrant shades, offering a long-lasting glossy shine. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty

node.text: As part of a series of colorful, playful images shot by @riccardo.apostolico for @guccibeauty: Fluide De Beauté Fini Naturel—a collection of natural finish liquid foundations available in 40 shades, Poudre De Beauté Mat Naturel, a buildable face powder that creates a unified complexion with a natural finish, and Poudre De Beauté Éclat Soleil to deliver a sun-kissed glow and a luminous looking finish. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: A still life shot of multiple Fluide De Beauté Fini Naturel foundations in different shades on a shiny green surface, light reflecting off their frosted glass bottles topped with a pale pink cap and embossed with the Gucci logo.
A still life shot of multiple Poudre De Beauté Mat Naturel Face Powders in different shades on a fuchsia surface, light reflecting off their open gold-toned click compacts with mirror inside the lid.

A still life shot of five Poudre De Beauté Éclat Soleil Powder bronzers against an orange background, balanced one on top of the other on a shiny orange surface, some open, some closed, light reflecting off their gold-toned click compacts with mirror inside the aqua blue lid.
Photo shared by Gucci Official on August 11, 2021 tagging @jenniferaniston. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.

node.text: A closer look at the fine leather craftsmanship behind each #GucciDiana handbag. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele

node.accessibility_caption: A still life shot of a finished pink leather Gucci Diana handbag with gold-toned Double G hardware, bamboo handles, fuchsia neon handle straps with Gucci lettering, and pink leather shoulder strap, on a white marble craftsman’s workbench against a blurred background.
A close-up shot of a craftsman using a hammer with wooden handle and metal head on a flap of pink leather detailed with gold-toned Double G hardware on a cut of pink leather.

A still life shot of multiple cuts of pink leather lying on a brown fabric cutting table with a roll of cut-out pink leather at the end, against the blurred background of metal stands holding rolls of white material.
